OIL SPILL RECOVERY, COAST GUARD (OIL SPILL LIABILITY TRUST FUND) Program and Financing (in millions of dollars) Identification code 69Â­8349Â­0Â­7Â­304 1997 actual 1998 est. 1999 est.
00.01 00.02 00.03 10.00
